---

<Layout title="JavaZone 2024 Partner">
    <article>
        <h1>JavaZone 2024 Partner</h1>
        <section>
            <h2>Information to registered partners</h2>
            <section class="block w-screen bg-black p-4 ml-[calc(-50vw+50%)] mr-[calc(-50vw+50%)] mt-4">
                <h2 class="text-3xl leading-9 font-semibold text-white mb-4 text-center text-red-text-color">
                    Partners in 2023
                </h2>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-10">
                    {partners
                        .sort(() => Math.random() - 0.5)
                        .map(partner => (
                            <a target="_blank" href={partner.homepageUrl}>
                                <Image
                                    height="10"
                                    width="10"
                                    class="h-16 w-40 transform transition-transform hover:scale-125"
                                    src={partner.logoUrl}
                                    alt={partner.name}
                                    style={{ padding: "5px" }}
                                />
                            </a>
                        ))}
                </div>
            </section>
            <h3>Partner tickets</h3>
            <p>You have four flexible stand tickets included in your partnership package. These are intended for stand personell, and does not give access to the talks. You must order tickets for everyone of you employees that wants to attend a talk (or if you have more than four who needs to be on the stand at once).</p>
            <p>Round robin distribution on tickets ordered by May 15th</p>
            <p>First come first served if tickets are still left after May 15th</p>
                <p>Price: 7 990,- NOK ex VAT and ticket fee</p>
            <ButtonLink
                    href="https://app.checkin.no/event/68811/javazone-2024-partner-tickets" target="_blank">Reserve partner tickets
                </ButtonLink>
            <h3>Stand allocation</h3>
            <p>We will start the start allocation in the beginning of April. We will contact your partner contact when it is your turn to pick your spot</p>
            <h3>Partner meeting #1</h3>
            <p>December 5th 2023</p>
            <iframe class="max-w-full max-h-52 md:max-h-full" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/891500045?h=7df20a26e4" width="640" height="360" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            <p><a href="https://vimeo.com/891500045">JavaZone 2024 Partner Meeting #1</a> from <a href="https://vimeo.com/user125589327">Macsimum AS</a>.</p>
            <p><a
                href="https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/wivcmqsj9a5058p8s3qcj/JZ2024PartnermeetingOne.pdf?rlkey=48d1t09xcfjqts9kfytk7aegb&dl=0" target="_blank">Slides</a></p>
            <h3>Partner meeting #2</h3>
            <p>March 12th 2024</p>
            <p><a href="https://vimeo.com/924608632/93124dc2a5?share=copy" target="_blank">Video recording</a></p>
            <p><a
                href="https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/7hjog348lc3w4h17pb37d/JavaZone2024-Partner-meeting-2.pdf?rlkey=mgh41p138d0khacxtnjcucc7m&dl=0" target="_blank">Slides</a></p>
            <h3>Partner meeting #3</h3>
            <p>Scheduled May 28th 2024</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Partner registration</h2>
            <p>We are currently sold out of partner packages. You can use the link below to register on the waiting list</p>

            <p><a target="_blank" href="https://app.checkin.no/event/65953/javazone-2024-partnership">Follow this
                link to register on waitinglist</a>. (This will send you to Checkin)</p>
            <p>There are three options to choose from, standard, restaurant and concept stand, where the two latter
                includes increased space to showcase yourself. See below for more details on the different
                packages.</p>
            <p>All partner packages are sold first come first served starting January 15th and as long as there are
                still packages left. If an option is sold out, you can register on a waiting list in case there are
                any cancellations</p>
            <p>You must choose one type of package. Once you complete the registration you will receive a
                confirmation of your choice. The formal contract and invoice will be sent to you later </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Partner packages</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions, please send us an e-mail at <a
                href="mailto:partner@java.no">partner@java.no</a>
            </p>
            <div class="packages">
                <section class="package">
                    <h3>Standard package</h3>
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-bold">Price</p>
                        <p>95 000,- NOK ex VAT</p>
                    </div>
                    <Image class="stand-image" alt="hello" src="/images/standard-stand.png" width="800"
                           height="450"/>
                    <p class="font-bold">Stand</p>
                    <p>6 square meters (3x2) with back and side wall, in the main conference hall.</p>

                    <p class="font-bold">Profiling</p>
                    <p>Logo with link on homepage and profiling in Oslo Spectrum</p>
                    <p class="font-bold">Stand ticket</p>
                    <p>4 flexible tickets for stand personnel.</p>
                    <p class="font-bold">Particiant tickets</p>
                    <p>Partner price on tickets for your colleagues</p>

                </section>
                <section class="package">
                    <h3>Concept stand</h3>
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-bold">Additional price</p>
                        <p>78 000,- NOK ex VAT</p>
                    </div>
                    <Image class="stand-image" alt="hello" src="/images/concept-stand.png" width="800"
                           height="450"/>
                    <p>All the benefits of the standard package.</p>
                    <p>Stand of 48 square meters (8X6 m)</p>
                    <p>Large space for showing off your own concept</p>
                    <p>Extremely limited – only <span class="font-bold">2</span> available</p>

                </section>
                <section class="package">
                    <h3>Restaurant stand</h3>
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-bold">Additional price</p>
                        <p>85 000,- NOK ex VAT</p>
                    </div>
                    <Image class="stand-image" alt="hello" src="/images/restaurant-stand.png" width="800"
                           height="450"/>

                    <p>All the benefits of the standard package with a restaurant stand</p>
                    <p>24 square meters (6x4 m) with a connected restaurant</p>
                    <p> Continuous food serving from your stand throughout the conference.</p>
                    <p>Menu in cooperation with event partners.</p>
                </section>

            </div>
        </section>
    </article>
</Layout>

<style>
    .package {
        margin: 1rem 0;
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: 16px;
        @apply shadow-2xl
    }

    @media screen and (min-width: 1400px) {
        .packages {
            display: grid;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        .package {
            gap: 1rem;
            margin: 0;
            display: grid;
            align-content: baseline;
        }
    }

    .partner-tickets {
        grid-column: 1 / end;
    }

    .stand-image {
        object-fit: cover;
        filter: saturate(0%) brightness(100%) contrast(80%);

    }
</style>
